<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Egloffstein, Landrichter zu Auerbach in der Oberpfalz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Fürsprache für Hermann Hetzelsdorfer, Bürger zu Nürnberg, in der Klage des Ulrich Twerchfelt wegen seines Guts zu Seidmar.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_20" id="8v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_20_r3l6">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del> <expan>Albrechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglofſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_20_r3l7">lantrichter cʒu Awerbach / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_20_r3l8">Lieber her <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> vns hat fürgelegt <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> <expan>Hetʒelſtöꝛff<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_20_r3l9">vnſer Burger vvie daʒ Jm vlrich Twerchfelt ſein gut cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_20_r3l10"><expan>Seÿte<ex>n</ex></expan> gelegen für ew auff daʒ lantgericht gen <expan>Aw<ex>r</ex>bach</expan> <expan>gelad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_20_r3l11">hab <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr dem ~ <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> vnſerm <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_20_r3l12">willen tʒum <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> fürderlıch vnd beholffen ſein wollet</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_20_r3l13">Als etc / das wöllen wir etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vȷ̃ ante <expan>Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> Anno vııȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_20" id="8v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Albrechte<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglofstein, lantrichter czu
                        Awerbach</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>, uns hat
                                                fürgelegt <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan>
<expan>Heczelstörff<ex>er</ex></expan>, unser
                                                burger, wie daz im Ulrich Twerchfelt sein gut czu
                                                  <expan>Seyte<ex>n</ex></expan> gelegen für ew auff
                                                daz lantgericht gen <expan>Aw<ex>r</ex>bach</expan>
<expan>gelad<ex>en</ex></expan> hab.
                                                  <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>, unserm
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen czum
                                                  <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> fürderlich und
                                                beholffen sein wollet, als etc. Das wöllen wir etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vi ante
                                                  <expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan> anno
                                                  viii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
